commit.title: Do not run 32-bit Windows builds on pull requests.
commit.message:
Do not run 32-bit Windows builds on pull requests.

I have never seen this build fail without the 64-bit Windows build
failing as well. So it is just a waste of time to test it on every
pull request and we are short in Windows test machines.
